<h2 id="moving-bootstrap-php-cache">Moving bootstrap.php.cache <a class="headerlink" href="new-dir-structure#moving-bootstrap-php-cache" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Speaking of <code>bootstrap.php.cache</code>, this now lives in the <code>var</code> directory. But wait,
<em>we</em> aren't responsible for this file. In fact, who created this in the first place?
Who put this in the <code>app</code> directory to begin with? It was Santa! Just kidding: it's
the SensioDistributionBundle, via one of these post install hooks in <code>composer.json</code>:</p>
