<p>We need to tell the SensioDistributionBundle that we want it to be built in <code>var</code>
instead of <code>app</code>. To do that, add a couple of new configuration lines in the <code>extra</code>
section of <code>composer.json</code>.</p>
<p>Add <code>"symfony-var-dir":</code> set to <code>"var"</code>, <code>"symfony-bin-dir":</code> set to <code>"bin"</code> and
<code>"symfony-tests-dir":</code> set to <code>"tests"</code>. The really important one here <code>symfony-var-dir</code>:</p>
